OL,5, Children in care were punched, locked  
OL,6, out naked and had vinegar poured on    
OL,7, cuts, according to reports that were   
OL,8, filed over three years before the homes
OL,9, were finally shut.                     
OL,11,FA BBC investigation has learned more   
OL,12,Fthan 100 concerns were logged at the   
OL,13,FDoncaster children's homes, which      
OL,14,Fretained a "good" Ofsted rating.       
OL,16,FLeaked documents also show Ofsted was  
OL,17,Falerted 40 times about incidents.      
OL,19,FThe regulator has now apologised, as   
OL,20,Fhas Hesley Group, which ran the homes. 
